    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"spell-description\">\n  <p>\n    <strong>School</strong>&nbsp;conjuration&nbsp;(summoning);\n    <strong>Level</strong>&nbsp;druid 1, hunter 1, ranger 1;\n    \n    \n    \n    \n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Casting Time</strong>&nbsp;1 round<br>\n    <strong>Components</strong>&nbsp;V, S, DF<br>\n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Range</strong>&nbsp;close (25 ft. + 5 ft./2 levels)<br>\n    \n    \n    <strong>Effect</strong>&nbsp;1d3 summoned creatures<br>\n    <strong>Duration</strong>&nbsp;1 round/level (D)<br>\n    <strong>Saving Throw</strong>&nbsp;none;&nbsp;<strong>Spell Resistance</strong>&nbsp;no<br>\n  </p>\n  <h2>Description</h2>\n  <p>This spell functions as summon nature's ally I, except you can summon 1d3 Tiny or smaller animals, such as bats, lizards, monkeys, rats, ravens, toads, or weasels. The summoned animals must all be the same type of creature.</p>\n</div>\n",
